## Problem Type
Live third-party petition page with degraded profile/identity presentation

## Why this matters
This is not a stale dead-link artifact. It is a live third-party public page that remains publicly discoverable, while part of the starter-account presentation appears broken, reduced, or anonymized. That combination should be tracked separately from both dead routes and fully intact live profile pages.

## Desired End State
- Search discovery: reduce or eliminate search visibility of the live petition page where it persists.
- Technical record: preserve documentation that the petition page remains live while the starter identity block appears degraded.
- Classification: distinguish this item from stale dead-route incidents and from fully intact live third-party profile pages.

